  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy, most importantly financial intermediation &#x2013; the efficient generation and allocation of savings to their most productive use.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy. More specifically, this includes Fund to support the development of affordable housing in Sub-Saharan Africa http://go.usa.gov/cuHE9. Partial or full payment guarantee issued to U.S. lenders with a portfolio of loans to foreign private-sector entities from target countries. The guarantee protects U.S. lenders from their customer&#x2019;s defaulting..</narrative>
